NAME
    Tasklicious - Activities management system based on tasks

DESCRIPTION
    This is a simple activities management system based on tasks
    created using Mojolicious::Lite.

    This is very useful and simple to use in a small and fast 
    projects.

MOTIVATION
    

FEATURES


RUNNING
    To start run this project is very easy.

        $ tasklicious.pl daemon
        Server available at http://127.0.0.1:3000.

